The paper deals with deep neural networks and their performance in image classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a new approach for detecting out-of-distribution inputs, which could fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) or cryptography and security (cs.CR).
